// Layout (rows 0..7 from bottom to top on screen):
//   row 0: black border (bottom)
//   row 1: shadow row   (dark shade)
//   rows 2-4: main fill (piece color)
//   row 5: left-edge highlight
//   row 6: top-left corner highlight
//   row 7: black border (top)
// ============================================================

